# {projectRoot}/repomix-output.md

this is the output of a tool called repomix. it formats the contents of a project into a single markdown file for use with LLMs. use this as a reference when making decisions or answering questions about the codebase.

Examples of when to use this:
- answering questions about how to implement a feature
- considering where to place a new file in the project